Modifications by Botond Bako (2026):
- Replaced zoom slider with zoom in/out buttons
- Redesigned UI with separate portrait and landscape layouts
- Replaced image buttons with Unicode text buttons
- Added exit button (top corner) and pause button (bottom corner)
- Added left-handed mode support for all new UI elements
- Added in-app language selector (Settings > Interface > Language)
- Added translations for 28 European languages:
  Bulgarian, Catalan, Czech, Danish, Dutch, Estonian, Finnish, French,
  Greek, Croatian, Icelandic, Italian, Latvian, Lithuanian, Norwegian,
  Polish, Portuguese, Albanian, Slovak, Slovenian, Serbian, Spanish,
  Swedish, Turkish, Ukrainian, Romanian, Hungarian, German
- Dynamic layout switching on orientation change
- Locale applied immediately on language change without restart
